    "body": "I have _n_ different related permissions to manage, Record101, Record102, Record103 in which one account may have Record rights for 101 and 102 but not 103, etc.  With RBAC I can set up _n_ permissions.  I *thought* I was going to append the number to the string, but that turns out to be expensive (string support is *still* terrible). So instead I might just use [integers and bitmasking](https://solidity.readthedocs.io/en/v0.4.25/types.html#integers). Those are fast, and the `const` variables are accessible through Web3.  Will append working code when working :/",
